short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds beautiful images and quotes to New Tab's background

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Refresh and uplift your mind with this extension.  When you open a new tab, images of beautiful nature and inspirational quotes in Chinese would be seen.  It is created by a tarot reader and spiritual healer Carlie from Hong Kong.
當你每次打開一個新 Chrome tab，一幅幅大自然的畫面，及發人心省的短句，滋養你的心靈，讓你醒神開始每一天！由香港塔羅占卜師及靈性療癒師 Carlie 策劃。IG：angel.circle.tarot
